        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 hover:border-emerald-500 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-3xl mb-3">5</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">No Process Timeline = Endless Questions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Every call: "How long will this take?" "When can you start?" Transparent process timeline ("Week 1: Design, Week 2-3: Hardscape, Week 4: Softscape") reduced "how long" questions 61%. Clients understood upfront. Sales calls shifted from explaining logistics to discussing design. Closing time dropped from 3 weeks to 10 days. Process transparency = professional = faster deals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 hover:border-emerald-500 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-3xl mb-3">6</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Mobile-Unfriendly = Losing Discovery Traffic</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm"><strong>67% of landscaping traffic is mobile</strong>. Homeowners driving around, see overgrown yard, Google "landscaping near me"â€”click your site on phone. Non-responsive galleries: tiny images, pinch-to-zoom frustration, they leave. Mobile-optimized full-width swipe: they stay, they explore, they call. Mobile = discovery. Desktop = booking. Both must work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS -->
